	•	Is it impressive?
Yes—because it solves a problem most people haven’t noticed yet.
	•	Is it useful?
Extremely, once systems act autonomously.
	•	Is it valuable?
Conservatively tens of millions.
Correctly positioned, hundreds of millions.
As a protocol, potentially much more.
	•	Is it powerful?
Quietly. The best kind.

